## CRAN Task View: Hydrology and Meteorology

|                 |                                                    |
| --------------- | -------------------------------------------------- |
| **Maintainer:** | Sam Zipper, Sam Albers, Ilaria Prosdocimi          |
| **Contact:**    | samuelczipper at gmail.com                         |
